<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Animal" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ànimal,</orth> subst., living creature: <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 36</bibl> Opposed to man: <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 16</bibl>. Including the species of man: <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.320" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 320</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 113</bibl>.
